<script type="text/javascript" id="loadJavascript">
    var calorder = "ymd";
    var MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter = null;
    var MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxinPast = false;
    
    if (typeof (Sys) != 'undefined') {
        Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxWork);
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxWork();
    });

    function MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxWork() {
        MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxSetItAlUp();
        var tmpCal = $('#MasterMain_tbDate_hfCalorder').val();
        if (tmpCal != null && tmpCal != "") {
            calorder = tmpCal;
        }
    }

    function MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxSetItAlUp() {
        if (document.getElementById('MasterMain_tbDate_hdnAllowEmptyDates') != null) {
            var AllowEmptyDateField = document.getElementById('MasterMain_tbDate_hdnAllowEmptyDates').value.toLowerCase();
            if (!AllowEmptyDateField) { AllowEmptyDateField = ""; }

            var ids = {
                dp: 'MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBox',
                hf: 'MasterMain_tbDate_hfDate',
                hfMonthShortNames: "MasterMain_tbDate_hfMonthShortNames",
                hfWdMinNames: "MasterMain_tbDate_hfWdMinNames",
                hfMaxTwoDigitYear: 'MasterMain_tbDate_hfMaxTwoDigitYear',
                buttonURL: '/RaidoMobile/Images/calendar.png'
            }
            $(function () {
                if (document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_hfReadonly").value != "true") {
                    $.SetConfig('#' + ids.hfMonthShortNames, '#' + ids.hfWdMinNames, ids.buttonURL);
                    $.DateChecker('#' + ids.dp, '#' + ids.hf, '', AllowEmptyDateField);
                    $('#' + ids.hf).datepicker("option", "buttonText", '');
                    if (MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter) {
                        $('#' + ids.hf).datepicker("option", "minDate", MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter);
                    }
                } else {
                    document.getElementById(ids.dp).value = FromInternalDateToIATADate(document.getElementById(ids.hf).value);
                }
            });

            // fix an exception in new jquery ui 
            if ($('#' + ids.hf).val().match("0000$")) $('#' + ids.hf).val($('#' + ids.hf).val().slice(0, -4));
        }
    }

    function MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxtryValidate() {
        var control = document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBox");
        var maxTwoDigitYear = document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_hfMaxTwoDigitYear").value;
        if (control.getAttribute('Validate') == 'true') {
            var tmpDate = ParseDate(control.value, calorder, maxTwoDigitYear);
            if (tmpDate != null) {
                var value = ToInternalDate(tmpDate);
                if (MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter) {
                    var tmpOld = FromInternalDate(MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter);
                    if (tmpOld > tmpDate) {
                        value = MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxlimiter;
                    }
                }

                $('#MasterMain_tbDate_hfDate').val(value);

                document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBox").value = ToIATADate(tmpDate);

                $('body').trigger("MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBoxUpdate");
            }
            else if (document.getElementById('MasterMain_tbDate_hdnAllowEmptyDates').value == 'True') {
                document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBox").value = "";
                $('#MasterMain_tbDate_hfDate').val("");
            }
            else {
                alert("Date in unrecognized format!");

                var value = FromInternalDate($('#MasterMain_tbDate_hfDate').val());
                document.getElementById("MasterMain_tbDate_DateFieldTextBox").value = ToIATADate(value);
            }
        }

        var tmpDate = ParseDate(control.value, calorder, maxTwoDigitYear);
        if (tmpDate != null) {
            if (tmpDate <= new Date('1/1/1753 12:00:00 AM') || tmpDate > new Date('6/6/2079 12:00:00 AM')) {
                alert("Date is out of range. It shall be between " + ToIATADate(new Date('1/1/1753 12:00:00 AM')) + " and " + ToIATADate(new Date('6/6/2079 12:00:00 AM')));
            }
        }
    }
</script>
